data.description: This delightful home in Evergreen boasts 5 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. It is conveniently located close to the interstate, Metra stations, and shopping centers. The main floor of the house features 3 bedrooms, with 2 additional bedrooms situated on the upper level. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and granite counter tops. The house offers ample space for entertaining with 3 living areas including a first-floor living room, a large recreation room in the basement, and a family room on the second level. The yard is fenced, and the home also features beautiful hardwood floors and much more.
